    (ii)corner lots, having their front on some intersecting or crossing street, avenue, lane, or
alley, and having their side upon the street, avenue, lane, or alley to be paved, shall be
counted for only ⅓ of the length of such side;

   (1)be deferred for such definite period of time as the said Director shall determine, not to
